Description: Description: Uses a generalized method to estimate the Potential Impact Fraction (PIF) 
  and the Population Attributable Fraction (PAF) from cross-sectional data. It creates 
  point-estimates, confidence intervals, and estimates of variance. In addition, it 
  generates plots for conducting sensitivity analysis.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
